Bo5 ku2 chiuN7 chun5 leng7 kau3, tui3 tang-pou7 Jiau2-a che7 chun5 seh8 kau3 Sin-ka-pho, tui3 hia ng3 chou2-kok chhut-phang5, ka7 Bi2-kok chiah e5 chun5 bo5 thang-a2 am3 bong-bong na2 toe7-ha7-sek, loh8 chun5-chhng u7 chhu tiu7-chhau2 na2 gu5-tiau5, hia chiu7-si7 goan2 e5 chhng5-phou, Sin-ka-pho e5 joah8 si7 100 tou7 khah ke7, sou2-i2 toa3 hit khoan2 chun5 chhng5 bo5 su che7 ti7 te7-gek8 e5 he2-nih, kau3 Tai7-tek kang2 e5 tiong-kan sou2 khoaN3 chou2-kok e5 hong-hoe3, put-kim3 sim-sng. Tui3 he2-chhia-lai7 khoaN3-tioh8 Kong2-to2 kho2-lin5 e5 cheng5-heng5, put-tek-put pi-than3 ngou2-siong7 kok, kun-kok e5 boat8-lou7. Chu2 Ia5-sou tui3 Ka-na2-soaN teng2 ui7-tioh8 Ia5-lou5-sat-leng2 lau5 bak8-sai2 thou2-khui3, na7 si7 Iu5-thai3 lang5 m7 bat Chu2 e5 chi2-i3 chiong I teng3 sip8-ji7-ke3, in e5 boat8-lou7, ia7 si7 an2-ni. Tak8 e5 chhia-cham7 moa2-moa2 to si7 boe2-boe7 e5 lang5, chheng7 oe5 tui3 he2-chhia e5 thang-a2 chhut-jip8, ti7 chou2-kok to7-gi7 oan5-choan5 siau-bo5, chi2-u7 san-ho5 chiau3 ku7 ti7-teh, m7-sin3 Seng3-keng e5 kok-bin5 sit8-chai7 kho2-lin5.
“Kong-gi7 hou7 pang-kok seng-koan5, kiN3 u7 choe7-ok e5 peh-siN3 siu7 leng5-jiok8.” (Chim-gian5 14:34) Goa2 keng-ke3 beh hoa e5 teng-sim e5 sin3-giong2 seng-oah8, si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 hou7 goa2 thiN lai5 e5 kau3-hun3, kap heng5-hoat8. Sit8-chai7 si7 khang-hi kho2-lin5 e5 thoan5-to7-chia2, put-phoe3 siu7 Siong7-te3 e5 lou5-pok8 Lun5-tun Seng3-keng hak8-iN7-tiuN2 Kha2-tah (Kater) Bok8-su e5 an3-chhiu2 le2.
18. Chai3 Khi2
Tng-si5 e5 Jit8-pun2 kok-bin5, ui7-tioh8 chit8-tng3-chiah8 cheng-thau5 khap8-hiah8 e5 cheng5-heng5, sit8-chai7 chin kho2-lin5. U7 chit8-jit8 khoaN3-kiN3 kui-kun5 e5 Jit8-pun2 hu7-jin5 ti7 pun3-so3-tui teh chhiau teh chhe7 sim2-mih8, te7 3 kok-bin5 phoe3-kip ka-lauh8 chham ti7 pun3-so3 e5 phu5-to5-koaN, in ti7 hia teh chhiau-chhe7, be7-su teh chhe7 po2-chioh8.
“PhaiN2 lang5 bo5 u7 peng5-an.”
“Hoan7-choe7 e5 leng5-hun5 tioh8 si2.”
“Kiah8 to--e5 beh in-ui7 to lai5 biat8-bo5.”
Seng3-keng e5 oe7 ho5-teng2 e5 hian7-sit8, thong3-kam2 hian7-kim chiaN3 si7 ui7-tioh8 hok-im phoe-mia7 kau-chian3 e5 si5. Goa2 ui7-tioh8 seng-oah8, choe3 in3-soat e5 goa7-kau, khai-si2 lou7-piN pou3-to7, soa3 pang-chan7 chhi7-lai7 e5 bou2 kau3-hoe7, siuN7 ai3 hou7 khah choe7 lang5 u7 hun7 Ki-tok e5 hok-im. Chiu7 hong2-bun7 kang-chhiuN2, hak8-hau7, piN7-iN7, khu-liu5-sou2 teng2 lai5 thoan5 hok-im. Tui3 Sam-leng5 tian7-ki e5 chit-giap8 hak8-hau7 300 e5 hak8-seng jiat8-jiat8 thoan5-to7, chong2-si7 it-khai3 bo5 siu sia7-le2. Tng si5 goa2 toa3 ti7 peng-sia3 e5 hong5-khong-tong7, mi5--si5 u7 chin-choe7 gia5-kang, iu5-ian5 (kap gia5-kang siang7-lui7) e5 khou2-chhou2, na7 loh8 hou7 chui2 oe7 lau5-jip8 lai5, mi5-si5 be7 khun3-tit, tioh8 eng7 poah8-thang2 hou3 chui2 chhut khi3, chong2-si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 pi7-pan7 chit8-keng siok-sia3 u7 kam2-sia7 put-chin7 e5 un-su3. Goa2 e5 sip8-koan3 si7 poaN3-mi5 khi2-lai5 ki5-to2, u7 chit8-mi5 2 tiam2-cheng ki5-to2 e5 si5, Chu2 ka7 goa2 kong2 “Li2 tioh8 khai-pan7 Seng3-keng hak8-hau7, iong2-seng5 thoan5-to7-chia2, thang siu-seng5 e5 choe7, kang lang5 chio2, Goa2 kiam2 bo5 beng7-leng7 li2, tioh8 iong2-kam2, tioh8 chong3-taN2.” Keh cha2-khi2 goa2 chiong chit e5 su7 tui3 hu7-jin5-lang5 kong2 iau-kiu5 i ki5-to2. Bo5 chiN5, bo5 kian3-tiok8-but8, koat-sim tui3 bo5 poaN3-hang7 lai5 iong2-seng5 thoan5-to7-chia2, chhin-chhiuN7 Chu2 Ia5-sou ka3-si7 12 e5 hak8-seng e5 khoan2. Siong7-te3 i2-goa7 bo5 sou2 oa2-kho3, it-khai3 boh8-tit khoa3-lu7, tok8-tok8 ban7-su7 tioh8 eng7 ki5-to2 khun2-kiu5 kap kam2-sia7, chiong lin2 sou2 kiu5--e5 pai5-liat8 ti7 Siong7-te3. (Hui-lip8-pi2 4:6)
Chong2-si7 ti7 4 thiap-poaN3 e5 hong5-khong-tong7 beh khui Seng3-keng hak8-hau7, sit8-chai7 si7 gong7-siuN7, kong2-beng5 su7-cheng5 si3-koe3 pai3-thok chioh chit8-keng sio bo5 liau2 e5 chhu3, tng-si5 siang7 khiam3 chhu3, sou2-i2 chit8 e5 bo5 mia5 e5 thoan5-to7-chia2 long2 bo5 lang5 beh chhap goa2. Tui3 thou2-khui3 e5 tiong-kan khia7 khi2-lai5, koh hak8-sip8 khiam-pi e5 lou7, tui3 Siong7-te3 e5 pang-chan7, tui3 Gu-le2 (Gray) sian-siN tit-tioh8 chit8 cho7 thian-bou7 chiu7 ti7 Ki-tok-kau3 sin-bun5 kong2-ko3 bou7-chip8 hak8-seng. Chi3-goan7 chia2 u7 70 lang5, eng7 ki5-to2 lai5 soan2 6 lang5. Chiah e5 lang5 u7 tui3 Chheng-sim u7 e5 tui3 Lok8-ji5-to2 tui3 choan5-kok tak8 sou2-chai7 lai5--e5, long2 hiap8-lek8 choe3 i2-a2, choe3-bin5-chhng5, tah thian-bou7, au7-poaN3 khng3 4 toe3 bin5-chhng5 choe3 siu-iong2 seng e5 khun3-pang5, cheng5-poaN3 choe3 kau3-sek kiam chip8-hoe7-sou2, ka7 chit8 e5 kiat-hut8 hoan7-chia2 ki5-to2, chiaN5-choe3 ki5-ian5 chit8 e5 song3-hiong lang5 chiong sin-khi2 8 thiap e5 peng-pang (Barrack) bo5 tiau5-kiaN7 chioh goan2. Tui3 che it-chhe3 e5 un-hui7 goan2 tang5-sim jiat8-jiat8 hian3 kam2-sia7 e5 ki5-to2.
Teng2-pou thak8 Sin5-hak8, e7-pou tiok8-ka hong2-bun7, phou2-kip8 Seng3-keng, am3-si5 tak8-am3 ke3-siok8 thian-bou7 pou3-to7. Chiah8-mih8 put-ko3 si7 thang chi2-ki e5 theng5-tou7, chong2-si7 tai7-ke saN pun-pheN chiah8 long2 bo5 lang5 kong2 put-chiok, ti7 song3 chiong e5 tiong-kan chiong sou2 u7 e5 chiN5 saN-pun choe3 sou2-hui3, long2 bo5 siu7 chiah8-hui3 a2-si7 hak8-hui3. Chu2 kong2 li2 khoaN3 khong-tiong e5 pe-chiau2, khong3-ia2 e5 pek-hap8-hoe, goan2 oan5-choan5 sin3-kho3 chit e5 Chu2 Ki-tok.
“Ki5-tiong bo5 khiam3-kheh e5 lang5.” (Su3-tou5 Heng7-toan7 4:34) Gu-le2 (Gray) sian-siN si7 ki5-to2 e5 seng3-tou5, siong5-siong5 sia2-phoe bian2-le7 goan2 “tioh8 seng3-kiat, tioh8 siu7 Sin5 chhiong-moa2, tioh8 tui-kiu5 hok8-heng,” koh kia3 choe7-choe7 i-hok8 hou7 goan2, chiau3 tak8 lang5 sou2 su-iau3 hun-phoe3, koh boe7 lai5 choe3 he2-sit8. In-ui7 cham2-jian5 kho2-khoan e5 thoan5-to7, sou2-i2 sin-bun5 ki3-chia2 lai5 hong2-bun7 goa2 khan ti7 sin-bun5. Chong2-si7 goa2 iau2-ku2 toa7-toa7 su-iau3 seng3-kiat, choe7 e5 kun iau2 teng3-tiau5 ti7 goa2 lai7-bin7, u3-oe3 e5 iok8-cheng5 iau2 u7 toa7 se3-lek8 teh koan2-hat goa2, sui-jian5 lau5-koaN7 chin7-lat8 chi2-u7 Siong7-te3 chai, Chu2 chhun I Seng3 Sin5 e5 kiam3 kat-le2 goa2 lai7-bin7 e5 lang5, hou7 goa2 hap8 I e5 lou7-eng7. U7 chit8-jit8 ti7 thian-bou7 siu7 seng3-chhan, chhin-chhiuN7 Sat-leng2 e5 che3-si Bek8-ki-se2-tek hou7 A-pek-lah8-han2 e5 seng3-chhan, chhu3-lai7 ki5-to2 kong2 “Goa2 si7 bi5-soe3, chhin-chhiuN7 piaN2-chhui3, chhiaN2 te7-it soe3 e5 un-hui7 hou7 goa2” chiu7 theh8 te7-it soe3-te3 e5 piaN2, na7-si7 eng5-kng chhan3-lan7 e5 Chu2 hian2-hian7 I e5 teng2 poaN3 sin, i lau5 bak8-sai2 an2-ni kian3-cheng3. Na7-si7 ti7 goa2 e5 sim-te2 u7 thiaN-kiN3 Chu2 e5 siaN. “KiaN2 ah! Goa2 sip8-ji7-ke3 e5 poe li2 oe7 siu7 mah?” Goa2 chin toa7 khiam-pi kong2 “Chu2 ah! Hit e5 khou2-lan7 e5 poe hou7 goa2, goa2 hoaN-hi2 seng5-siu7.”
Teh siuN7 si7 sim2-mih8 su7? Chu2 beh hou7 goa2 e5 khou2-poe si7 sim2-mih8? Chiu7-si7 kau3-taN m7-bat keng-giam7 tioh8, hui-siong5 thong3-khou2 seng3-gian5 (Siong7-te3 e5 oe7) e5 chhi3-lian7, kiat-cheng7 leng5-hun5 e5 he2-iam7. Tng-si5 u7 chit8 e5 chheng-lian5 khoaN3 Ki-tok-kau3 sin-bun5 lai5 beh jip8-hak8, chit e5 chheng-lian5 e5 sin-hun7 si7 chian5 kho 2 hoan7, ia7 be7 thang tng2-khi3 kiN3 pe7-bu2 e5. Chong2-si7 ka7 i kong2 u7 chian5-kho e5 lang5 m7-chun2 jip8-oh8, bo5-lun7 an2-choaN2 ka7 i kong2 to m7 li7-khui, tui3 an2-ni goa2 chiu7 ka7 choe3 po2-cheng3-jin5 hou7 i khi3 iu5-chhat-tiam3 chiah8 thau5-lou7, chong2-si7 m7-khi3 iu5-chhat-tiam3, chai3 saN ai3 kiu5 hou7 i jip8-oh8, boe7 kham-tit i kou-chiaN5 chiu7 chun2 i jip8-oh8. An2-ni siu-iong2-seng piN3 choe3 7 e5 lang5, hun-choe3 2 ui7 toa3, khai-si2 siu7-giap8. Bo5 loa7-ku2 chit e5 chheng-lian5 siu7 iu2-hek8 koh choe3 phaiN2-su7, sim be5 loan7 soa3 phah chit8 e5 siu-iong2-seng. Tui3 an2-ni hak8-iN7 koat-teng7 theng5-pan7, hou7 hak8-seng long2 tng2-khi3.
Chiong5-cheng5 Kou2-kok hiaN i-seng khoaN3 i choe3 choat8-cheng3 teh theng3-hau7 si2, tit-tioh8 i-ho2, chit pai2 u7 hian3 toa7 pit e5 chiN5, sou2-i2 hou7 chiah e5 hiaN-ti7 long2 u7 kau3-giah8 e5 lou7-hui3. Goan2 chin thong3-sim, kiu5 Siong7-te3 lin5-bin2; teh theng3-hau7 chai3 khai-pan7 e5 jit8. Na7-si7 chit e5 chheng-lian5 na2 phaiN2, soa3 kiah8 to chiong goan2 sou2 u7 e5 chiN5 kap mih8 long2 chhiuN2 khi3, choe3-au7 e5 koan-thau5 keng2-chhat chhut-chhiu2, chheng-lian5 koaiN loh8 kaN. Sui-jian5 taN bo5 poaN3-hang7, iau2-ku2 jiat8-sim ki5-to2 ng3-bang7 chit e5 chheng-lian5 oe7 hoe2-kai2, ah! Sip8-ji7-ke3 sit8-chai7 chin tang7.
