19. Ia5-ho5-hoa I2-lek8
Thian-bou7 ti7 chit8 sou2-chai7 tah poaN3-ni5, tang-thiN kau3 chiu7 siu khi2-lai5. Tui3 Siong7-te3 e5 un-hui7 chhun-thiN hak8-iN7 chiu7 koh khai-si2, ti7 4 thiap e5 pang5-keng thak8-chheh, siu2 le2-pai3, ti7 ke-lou7 lou7-piN pou3-to7, long2 bo5 lang5 kong2 put-peng5, chit8 keng le2-pai3-tng5 si7 na2 bong7-tong7 (calacombs, chhou-tai7 e5 kau3-hoe7 tng Lo5-ma2 te3-kok toa7 khun2-tiok8 e5 si5, sin3-tou5 chiu7 bih ti7 bong7-tong7 lai7 le2-pai3) e5 hong5-khong-ho5, 10 goa7 lang5 chiu7 tiN7 khi2-lai5, kan-ta hoe7-chiong3 e5 chhoan2-khui3, chhu3-lai7 to oe7 hou7 hip-joah8. Bu5-i3 tiong tui3 Siong7-te3 ai-kiu5 “SiuN2-su3 chhu3-theh8” chit si5 khi2 tai7-ke ki5-kiu5 lang5 teh chiok-hok, loa7 choe7 lang5 kim3-chiah8 thang jit8 ti7 Mou5-ia5-soaN ki5-to2, a2-si7 thong-mi5 ti7 soaN-lai7 ki5-kiu5 Siong7-te3, chiah e5 hiaN-ti7 ki5-to2 kau3 sau-siaN, iau2-ku2 piaN3-mia7 teh ki5-to2, ti3-kau3 ke3-lou7-lang5 theng5-kha lai5 thiaN, keng2-koaN liah8 hun2 si7 sat-jin5 su7-kiaN7 chu3-sin5 teh thiaN. Tui-kiu5 hoe2-kai2 kap seng3-kiat, tai7-ke long2 be7 ki3-tit chit se3-kan, it-tit8 chin3-cheng5 ng3 thian-tng5. U7 chit8 jit8 chit8 e5 peng5-iu2 chhiaN2 goa2 khi3 bian7-hoe7, si7 chit8 ui7 bi7-sin3-chia2 sit8-giap8-ka siu7 Siong7-te3 kam2-tong7. “Lin2 jiat8-sim teh chong-kau3 un7-tong7, bo5 chhu3 chin khou2-sim houN3! Long5-ti5 lou7 ti7 iuN5-chhai5 hak8-iN7 e5 hau7-sia3, khi3 khoaN3-mai7, na7 ho2 chiu7 poaN jip8-khi3.”
“Goa2 bo5 chiN5 bo5 hoat-tou7.”
“Bo5 chiN5 bo5 iau3-kin2, na7 u7 chiN5 chiah choe7 chio2 heng5.” Chin-chiaN3 ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 soaN u7 pi7-pan7 Ia5-lou7-sat-leng2 e5 tian7. Toa7 kam2-sia7 o-lo2 Siong7-te3, chheng-khi3 seng3-tian7, iuN5-chhai5 hak8-iN7 theng5-pan7, choe3 thiau3-bu2-tiaN5, si3-ke3 chin lah-sap, na2 ki5-to2 na2 chheng-sau3, soa3 keh-keng hun choe3 hak8-iN7 kap le2-pai3-tng5. I2-toh, mng5-thang ki5-thaN tak8-hang7 long2 goan2 ka-ki7 choe3. Sit8-chai7 si7 khoai3-lok8 e5 thian-kok chok-giap8. Chong2-si7 goan2 si7 Ki-tok-tou5, u7 kam2-kak tioh8 heng5-che3 e5 tang7-taN3. Khai-si2 “Kiu5 Chu2 siuN2-su3” io5-tang7 thian-pang5 e5 ki5-to2. Ui7-tioh8 chit keng chhu3, ui7-tioh8 thou2-toe7, kap boe2 keh-piah e5 te7, tian2-khui kim3-chiah8 ki5-to2, toa7 un-hui7 e5 Chu2 eng7 thun-lun2 thiaN goan2 e5 ki5-to2, jiat8-jiat8 e5 hian3-kim saN soa3 lai5, ai7 si7 tui3 kok-goa7 lai5 hian3--e5, tui3 bi2-ang3 kau3 tau7-iu5, iam5 long2 khang-khang si7 siong5-su7, song3-hiong e5 seng-oah8 ia7 koan3-si3, chiah8-mih8 chi2 u7 chhin-chhiuN7 I2-li7-a sin3-kho3 siong7-te3 chhe ou-a lai5 kiong-kip, che si7 goan2 e5 jit8-siong5 seng-oah8. Jiat8-jiat8 e5 lou7-piN thoan5-to7, Chu2-jit8-oh8 hak8-seng u7 300 lang5 i2-siong7, si7 chin khou2-koan e5 thoan5-to7 hong-keng2. “Siong7-te3 beh ka-ki7 pi7-pan7 sio-che3 e5 iuN5-ko.” (Chhong3-se3-ki3 22:8)
20. Seng3-chian3
Hit si5 Siong7-te3 u7 sang3 2 e5 soe3-kiaN2 lai5 goan2 e5 sou2-chai7. Chit8 e5 si7 in2-iong5-chia2 chian5-kho hoan7 e5 kiaN2, eng5-iong2 bo5 kau3, chin hi-jiok8, iau2 chit8 e5 si7 cheng-sin5-piN7 hoan7-chia2 e5 kiaN2, seng3-keh be7 su cheng-seN e5. Hit e5 sin-the2 soe-jiok8 e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 sim u3-ju5 thang kho2-lin5. Tiam2-sim e5 si5, goa2 ka7 theh8 piaN2 khi2 lai5, chiu7 bak8-chiu gin5 ouN3-ouN3 pi2 kun5-thau5-bu2 beh cheng goa2. 5 geh8 thiN e5 jit8-thau5-e7 chheng7 4-5 nia2 saN, hu7-jin5-lang5 ka7 i thng3 chit8 nia2 khi2-lai5, chek-si5 tioh8 kam2-mou7 khi2 he5-ku. Hou7 hit 2 e5 gin2-na2 toa3 tiaN5 nih8 thit-tho5, hit e5 hi-jiok8 e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 chok-koai3, iau2 hit e5 chiu7 ka7 i ka7 chhiu2, 2 e5 khiu2 teh khau3, be7 bian2-tit sim-koaN niu5 thiaN3. Hu7-jin5-lang5 choe3 tiong-sim hiah e5 lu2-chu2 hian3-sin tui3 cho3 chou7-chhiu2, chin7-sim cheng-sin5 kau3-iok8 kap kian7-khong chi2-to7, Chu2 Ia5-sou e5 ka3-si7 choe3 tiong-sim, kong2 Seng3-keng e5 ka3-si7 hou7 in thiaN, eng7 un-loan2 e5 thiaN3 lai5 iong2-iok8. Hit e5 eng5-iong2 sit-tiau7 e5 gin2-na2, keng-ke3 6 ko3-geh8 chiu7 iong2 khi2-lai5, bin7 ia7 na2 eng-hoe e5 hun2-ang5 sek, seng3-chit ia7 chiam7-chiam7 beng5-long2, oe7 gim5-si ki5-to2.
Chong2-si7 hit e5 he5-ku gin2-na2 long2 be7 iong2 khi2-lai5 chin khoa3-lu7, kiat-hut8-seng3, na7 phak8 tioh8 jit8 chiu7 hoat-jiat8, sau3 to2-chhng5 2, 3 le2-pai3, hu7-jin5-lang5 chiu7 aiN7 khi3 hou7 i-seng khoaN3, i-seng hoan-hu3 “Chit e5 gin2-na2 chin jiok8, kaN2 si7 kiat-hut8-seng3, khah ho2 tioh8 khi3 chio3 kng-soaN (Ronlgen ray)” mi5-si5 lau5 chhin3-koaN7 chhu3-lai7 tioh8 ka7 i chhit 2, 3 pian3 ka7 i oaN7-saN. Long2 bo5 siu sia7-le2, si7 peh8-peh8 e5 hong7-su7, chi2-u7 ng3 thiN ki5-kiu5 “Ia5-ho5-hoa ah, si7 Li2 e5 soe3-kiaN2, kiu5 Li2 pou2 khiam3-kheh” u7 chit8-mi5 goa2 bang7-kiN3, chit-be2 soe3-be2 tok8-choa5 kiaN2 ti7 lou7-piN, goa2 eng7 oe5 ka7 i that-khi3, na7-si7 i it-tit8 thiau3 khi2-lai5, thou3-chhut tok8-khi3 kap goa2 ti2-khong3, sui si7 se3-boe2 tok8-choa5, put-lun7 an2-choaN2 ka7 that ka7 kong3 to long2 bo5 siu7 siong, hoan2-tng2 khui-chhui3 kap goa2 ti2-khong3.
SiuN7 kong2 5 chhioh e5 lam5-chu2-han3 khah su chit8 be2 tok8-choa5 hiah bo5 iong2-khi3, “kiN3-na7 oa2-kho3 jiok8-the2, sim li7-khui Ia5-ho5-hoa e5 lang5 tioh8 siu7 chiu3-chou2” m7-si7 tok8-choa5, si7 mou5-kui2. Tioh8 ti7 Chu2 Ia5-sou e5 seng3-mia5 kap i kau-chian3. “Ti7 Ia5-sou Ki-tok e5 seng3-mia5 beng7-leng7 li2 the3 khi3” kiah8 khi2 chhiu2 an2-ni hoah e5 si5, tok8-choa5 chiu7 chau2-jip8 chioh8-chhiuN5 lai7. Ah, kai-chai3, thou2 chit8 e5 toa7-khui3, chhiN2 khi2-lai5 chit8 khoaN3, cha-bou2 gin2-na2 teh khong7-khong7 sau3, ah hai7 lah, koh lai5 lah! Ti7 Sin5-hak8-hau7 si5-tai7, hong3-ka2 e5 jit8 goa2 chiu7 khi3 hong2-bun7 kiat-hut8 liau5-iong2 sou2, a2-si7 chhiah-li7, tng5-a2 piN e5 piN7-iN7 ui7-tioh8 piN7-khou2 e5 peng5-iu2 hoaN7-chhiu2 ki5-to2, put-lun7 sim2-mih8 piN7 long2 m7 kiaN.
Chong2-si7 khoaN3-kiN3 chit e5 se3-kiaN2 jit8-jit8 tit8-tit8 siau-san2, sim chin iu-ut. Chhu3-lai7 ti7 gin2-na2 e5 chim2-thau5 piN ki5-to2 “Siong7-te3 oe7 i-ti7 tak8 hang7 e5 piN7, chong2-si7 kong2 peh8-chhat8 e5, oan-ke e5, phaiN2-sim e5, I bo5 beh pang-chan7, sou2-i2 li2 tioh8 hoe2-kai2, goa2 ia7 tioh8 hoe2-kai2” kong2 an2-ni 2 lang5 lau5 bak8-sai2 ki5-to2 e5 si5, Chu2 chhun seng3 chhiu2, hian2-chhut i-ti7 e5 sin5-jiah. Chin si7 po2-poe3 thiN e5 ka3-si7, 5 ni5-ku2 chaiN2-iuN7 khou2-sim teh hok8-sai7 chit e5 soe3-kiaN2? Siong7-te3 chai, u7 chit8 pai2 goa2 beh chhut khi3 sun5-hoe5 thoan5-to7 chin chai u7 Sat-tan3 bih ti7 mng5-piN beh hou7 goan2 toa7 chai-e7, ko2-jian5 chhin-chhiuN7 Iok-pek e5 ka-chok8 hou7 Sat-tan3 phah kau3 hiam2-hiam2 si2, chhin-siN e5 lau7-bu2 lai5 saN-tham3, hiam5 kong2 “chhiaN3 lang5 io be7 eng7-tit, khah kong2 ia7 tioh8 ka-ki7 io” chhu3-lai7 am3-am3 khau3 koh u7 chit8 pai2 chit8 e5 sin3-tou5 lai5 saN an-ui3, tng2-khi3 tui3 pat8 lang5 kong2 “bo5 ng3-bang7 lah!” tui3 chit ku3 oe7, chin thang kiaN mou5-kui2 e5 he2-chiN3 sia7 tui3 goan2 lai5. Chi2-u7 eng7 bak8-sai2 te2-moa2 goan2 e5 phe-long5, ki5-kiu5 Siong7-te3 e5 lin5-bin2. Chong2-si7 chiah po2-poe3 e5 kau3-hun3, si7 sim2-mih8 to be7 thang the3-oaN7 siong7-te3 e5 un-su3, an2-ni khoaN3-phoa3 se3-kan, chhin-chhiuN7 ng5-kim keng-ke3 he2 e5 go5-lian7, chiah e7 hap8 Chu2 e5 lou7-eng7, soe3-kiaN2 iong2 khi2-lai5 lah, e5-hng cha2-khi2 kam2-sia7 ki5-to2. 2 lang5 long2 heng5 in e5 pe7-bu2.
“Sou2-i2 lang5 na7 chheng-khi3 ka-ki7 thoat-li7 chiah e5, chiu7 beh choe3 kui3-khi3 e5 khi3-ku7, chiaN5 seng3, hap8 ti7 Chu2-lang5 e5 lou7-eng7, pian7-pian7 thang choe3 tak8 hang7 e5 ho2-su7.” (II The5-mou5-thai3 2:21)
21. Siong7-te3 E5 Se3-Kiann2
Hit-taip8 liau2-au7 chhoa7 chit8 e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 lai5, lau7-pe7 ui7-tioh8 su-iaN5 pho3-san2, chit e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 ti7 hit khoan2 pi-kek8 e5 tiong-kan chhut-si3, chit8-tou7 e5 kia3-seng-thang5 hoan7 tioh8 tng5-iam7, pang3-huih, cho3-li7, chin siong-tiong, chhim-sin3 Sin5-ju2, sin3 Siong7-te3 oe7 i-ho2 chiu7 ka7 i in2-siu7, tak8-jit8 piaN3-mia7 ki5-to2 kap khan3-hou7. Chu2 Ia5-sou e5 Seng3-chhiu2 kiat-cheng7 chit e5 gin2-na2 e5 sin-the2, hian2-chhut i-ti7 e5 un-hui7.
Goa2 tit-kiu3 e5 tong-chhou chiu7 kian-koat beh it-seng tok8-sin hok8-sai7 Siong7-te3, ia7 kau3 38 he3 an2-ni kiaN5 sip8-ji7-ke3 e5 lou7, ti7 kho2-phaN3 Tai7 Tang-a chian3-cheng e5 tiong-cham7 Chu2 chi2-si7 goa2 chit8-ui7 chi2-be7, chit-pai2 ti7 bin5-bang7, koh chit8-pai2 ti7 iN7-siong7 ka7 goa2 kong2 “Chit e5 si7 li2 e5 loe7-chou7, theh8 lai5 chiah8” hit si5 goa2 ti7 lian7-seng5-sou2 chheng2-ka2 2 tiam2-cheng, ku2-heng5 kiat-hun-sek, chu7 an2-ni khi3 Jiau2-a. Na7-si7 Chu2 e5 oe7 “Siong7-te3 ti7 hit tiong-kan, siaN5 tek-khak boe7 io5-tang7.” (Si-phian 46:5) Lang5 oe7 chian3-si2, siaN5 oe7 sio-khi3, chong2-si7 chit e5 kiat-hun si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 teng7--e5, bo5-lun7 u7 sim2-mih8 chai-ho7 to be7 pho3-hoai7. 40 he3 e5 si5, goa2 choe3 in2-iong5-chia2 kui kok kap chi2-be7 saN-kap toa3, chit8-sim chit8-i3 hok8-sai7 Siong7-te3. Goa2 seng5-sim sun5-sun5 tui3 chi2-be7 kong2-beng5 goa2 e5 sim-cheng5, “Kok-ka teh beh biat8-bo5, chi2-u7 Chu2 Ia5-sou koh-oah8 e5 koan5-leng5 chiah oe7 chin2-kui3 chit e5 kok-ka, goa2 siu7 Chu2 hok8-heng e5 tiau3-beng7, lip8-se3 cho3 Na2-se3-jiN2 lang5, chiong-sin tok8-sin hok8-sai7 Siong7-te3, sou2-i2 lan2 e5 kiat-hun m7 si7 jiok8-the2 e5 kiat-hun, si7 leng5-tek kiat-hun. Chu2 Ia5-sou pun2-sin choe3 mui5-lang5 seng3 e5 kiat-hun, eng7 oan5-choan5 seng3-kiat Seng3 Sin5 e5 hap8-it toa7-toa7 choe3 Siong7-te3 e5 kang.”
U7 si5-kan chiu7 ka7 i ke2-beng5 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7, pi7-pan7 choe3 kau-chian3 e5 lou7-eng7, Seng3 Chu2 hou7 goan2 chit8 e5 se3-kiaN2, si7 thiN e5 siuN2-su3, ui7-tioh8 an2-ni chiu7 in2-chhoa7 se3-kiaN2 jip8 ti7 Seng3-keng e5 seng-oah8. Khi2-chhou ti7 chi2-be7 e5 kha-thau5-u teng2 chit8-ku3 chit8-ku3 ka3 i ki5-to2, na7 bo5 ki5-to2 bo5 thang chiah8-png7, ia7 bo5 tiam2-sim, chu2-png7 e5 si5-kan na7 kau3, chiu7 lai5 toh-kha liam7 “Men Men” (chiu7-si7 A-men) 3-4 he3 chiu7 e7 ka-ki7 ki5-to2, m7-ku2 u7 si5 ia7 e7 put-hok8 m7 ki5-to2, chi2-be7 chiu7 chhu than2-a2 he7 kha-thang2 hou7 se3-kiaN2 che7, “bo5 ki5-to2 e5 gin2-na2 m7 hou7 i chiah8 cha2-khi2-tng3. Chiah8-mih8 saN-khou3 long2 si7 Ia5-sou sou2 su3, sou2-i2 boe7 ki3-tit ki5-to2 e5 gin2-na2 m7-hou7 i” kong2 liau2 chiu7 ka7 i koaiN ti7 chhng-khou3, bo5 ku2 chiu7 toa7 siaN khau3, liam5-piN kong2 “Ma-ma, goa2 m7 tioh8, beh ki5-to2 lah, chhiaN2 sia3-bian2 goa2” kong2 liau2 chiu7 ki5-to2.
Chit khoan2 su7 10 jit8 hoan2-hok chit8 pai2, na7 si7 chi3-ho2 e5 Siong7-te3 gin2-na2 na7 ki5-to2, tek-khak u7 ho2 e5 chiok-hok, khi2-chhou na2 chhin-chhiuN7 tui3 khong-khi3 kong2 oe7 gin2-na2 chin bo5 ai3, kau3 5-6 he3 chiu7 u7 ki5-to2 e5 the2-giam7, kau3 7-8 he3 chiu7 1 jit8 ki5-to2 5 pai2. Chong2-si7 iau2 ku2 siong5-siong5 to3-toaN5 pin5-toaN7 ki5-to2.
U7 si5 chhu3-lai7 an2-ni kong2 “M7 ki5-to2 e5 gin2-na2 goa2 bo5 ai3, kin-a2-jit8 hak8-hau7 tng2-lai5, chheh-pau theh8-le3 chu7 an2-ni khi3 soaN-nih8, khi3 soaN-tong7 chioh8-thau5-khang long2 ho2, m7 bian2 tng2-lai5,” kong2 an2-ni chiu7 sang3 gin2-na2 chhut-khi3, e7-pou 2 tiam2 e5 si5, chiau3 peng5-siong5 khui au7-mng5 kong2 “Goa2 tng2-lai5 lah.” Chhu3-lai7 chiu7 chhut-khi3 ka7 i kong2 “M7-bian2 tng2-lai5 ho2”, “goa2 ti7 hak8-hau7 siuN7-lai5 siuN7 khi3, bo5-lun7 u7 siaN2-su7 to beh ki5-to2 lah, chhiaN2 sia3-bian2 goa2.” Chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni gin2-an2 e5 sim, cheng7-cheng7 kui ng3 Siong7-te3. Ui7-tioh8 6-7 e5 hok8-heng e5 hiap8-lek8-chia2, ui7-tioh8 Chu2-jit8-oh8 e5 peng5-iu2 sui5-e5 kio3 mia5 lai5 ki5-to2. Hian7-kim ui7-tioh8 Bi2-kok kui2 chap8 lang5 ki5-to2 bo5 soah.
Goa2 siuN7 se3-chiuN7 e5 lang5 it-bi7 koan-sim hak8-bun7 e5 kau3-iok8, ti3-i3 chheng7-chhah, eng5-iong2, ui7-tioh8 chiong-lai5 e5 chhut-sin hi-seng it-chhe3, tui3 thian-kok choan5-jian5 bo5-ian5. Loa7-nih8 u7 hak8-bun7, na7 bo5 keng3-pai3 Siong7-te3, bo5 thiaN3 chhu3-piN, hit khoan2 e5 hak8-bun7, kiam2 oe7 tit-tioh8 chiok-hok? KiaN2-ji5 kiau-ngou7 liah8 choe3 pe7-bu2 khah gau5. Bo5 u7 Ia5-sou e5 sia7-hoe7, hak8-hau7, ka-teng5 si7 ho5-teng2 e5 khou2-lin5. Tioh8 thiaN Siong7-te3 thou2-khui3 e5 siaN. Chit e5 se3-kai3 si7 Siong7-te3 e5, tak8 e5 lang5 long2 si7 Siong7-te3 chhong3-cho7 e5, khi3-sak cho7-but8 Chu2 Siong7-te3 e5 seng-oah8 u7 chai-e7, ti7 chit khoan2 e5 hian7-se3, goan2 kian-sim beh kau3-iok8 hit ho7 ui7-tioh8 Siong7-te3 kap jin5-ai3 kap sin3-giong2 goan7 hian3 it-chhe3, lai5 se2 chhu3-piN e5 kha, hoaN-hi2 hong7-su7 e5 gin2-na2.
Sou2-i2 goan2 e5 ka-teng5 si7 Siong7-te3 tiong-sim seng-oah8. Chong2-si7 gin2-na2 chit8-e7 khi3 hak8-hau7 chiu7 oh8 kong2 peh8-chhat8, khoaN3 peng5-iu2 teh oan-ke, khoaN3 pat8 e5 peng5-iu2 ai3 e5 mih8 chiu7 boe2, chiu7 thau-theh8 chhu3-lai7 gin5-te7-a2 e5 chiN5 khi3 be2 sou2 ai3 e5 mih8, chha-put-to tak8-jit8 ti7 hak8-hau7 to si7 siu7 phaiN2 e5 kam2-hoa3, sou2-i2 chhu3-lai7 ti3-i3 ka3-si7 gin2-na2, u7 si5 1 jit8 bo5 hou7 i khi3 hak8-hau7, ka7 i koaiN toa3 pang5-keng, bo5 hou7 i chiah8, kio3 i ka-ki7 hoan2-seng2. Se3-kiaN2 gin2-na2 jit8-jit8 hiong3-siong7, oe7 hiau2 hun-piat8 ho2 phaiN2. U7 chit8 jit8 goa2 teh ki5-to2, khoaN3-kiN3 se3-kiaN2 ti7 hau7-tiaN5 hou7 sia7-hoe7 ok e5 kiaN-lang5-chui2 phah la5-sam5, siu7 phaiN2 e5 kam2-hoa3 tng2-lai5, hit si5 Chu2 kong2: “Chhin-chhiuN7 ti7 Iok-tan3-ho5 se2 seng-khu 7 pai2, chhin-chhiuN7 eng7 chui2 se2 seng-khu, li2 tioh8 tak8-jit8 eng7 Siong7-te3 e5 thiaN3 ka7 li2 e5 se3-kiaN2 se2-le2.”
U7 chit8 ui7 hu7-jin5-lang5 mng7 chhu3-lai7 kong2, “ChaiN2-iuN7 teh kau3-iok8 gin2-na2?” Chhu3-lai7 in3 “Chong-kau3 kau3-iok8!” Hu7-jin5-lang5 kong2, “Chong-kau3 kau3-iok8 bo5 chhai2-kang, ma7 u7 m7 chiaN5 bok8-su kiaN2--e5.” Chin u7 ke3-tat8 e5 kau3-hun3, chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni Chu2 Ia5-sou mi5-jit8 choe3 goan2 ka-teng5 e5 tiong-sim, goan2 khak-sin3 koh-oah8 e5 Chu2 eng7 I e5 eng5-iau7 si5-si5 kap goa2 tong5-chai7. Chu2 kong2: “Chit ke si7 seng3 ka-teng5, chhin-chhiuN7 Iok-sek Ma2-li7-a e5 ka-teng5 u7 Chu2 Ia5-sou, chiaN5 choe3 seng3 ka-teng5, lin2 e5 ka-teng5 ia7-si7 an-ni.” Chan3-bi2 Ia5-sou Ki-tok e5 Pe7 Siong7-te3. Au7-lai5 hak8-hau7 e5 sian-siN mng7 kong2 “Li2 toa7-han3 beh choe3 sim2-mih8?” In3 kong2 “Choe3 lu2 bok8-su.” Tui3 thiN lai5 thiaN chit ku3 oe7 e5 Siong7-te3, chiaN3 si7 chit e5 gin2-na2 e5 Pe7.
“Ia5-sou e5 ti3-hui7 kap ni5-he3 na2 ke-thiN, Siong7-te3 kap lang5 na2 thiaN3 i.” (Lou7-ka 2:52)
22. Thoan5-to7 E5 Choan2-ki
Hak8-iN7 tak8-jit8 teh hun3-lian7 thian-bou7 pou3-to7, lou7-piN pou3-to7 bo5 lang5 e5-hng5, siu-iong2 seng si7 toa3 ti7 thian-bou7, lu2-chu2 hian3-sin chia2 boe2-chhai3, chhu3-lai7 pan7 koe3-ke3 kap chhui-su7. Goa2 ti7 thian-bou7 au7 am3-am3 ki5-to2, kiu5 Siong7-te3 e5 koan5-leng5 kang3-loh8 ti7 siu-iong2 seng e5 kian3-cheng3 kap soat-kau3, u7 chit8 am3 bo5-i3-tiong thiaN-kiN3 Seng3 Sin5 e5 siaN chhin-chhiuN7 chheng-thian phek-lek8 chit8-iuN7: “Li2 e5 mia5 si7 Iok-han7, li2 e5 mia5 si7 Iok-han7.” “Li2 tioh8 ka7 i ho7 mia5 kio3 Iok-han7.” Si7 thiN-sai3 ka7 Sat-ka-li7-a kong2 e5, chong2-si7 goa2 to bo5 kiu5, iau2-ku2 Siong7-te3 ho7 chit e5 mia5 “Iok-han7”. Thian-bou7 pou3-to7, chit8 e5-hng kui2-na7 chap8 lang5 koat-sim, na7 si7 chiah e5 siu-iong2 seng chhut-lat8 hong2-bun7 ia7 bo5 ke2-chi2, ku2-ku2 e5 thian-bou7 pou3-to7 theng5-chi2, bo5-lun7 loh8-seh e5 e5-hng, a2-si7 iam7-jiat8 e5 joah8-thiN, goan2 koat-toan3 bo5 theng5-chi2 lou7-piN pou3-to7. Loh8-sng seh tang3 e5-hng5 si5 e5 soat-kau3, ia7 lau5-koaN7 kau3 lai7-saN e7 chun7-tit, piaN3-mia7 teh thoan5-to7, na7-si7 che si7 chhin-chhiuN7 Ho5-liat8-soaN e5 toe7-tang7, Siong7-te3 e5 seng3 chi2-i3 bo5 ti7 chia, iu5-goan5 tioh8 to3-tng2 kau3 eng7 Sin5-ju2 choe3 bu2-khi3 Su3-tou5 Heng5-toan7 e5 thoan5-to7, Seng3 Sin5 cheng7-cheng7 chhui-pek goa2 kau3 bak8-pang5 e5 ki5-to2.
Hit si5-chun7 Bi2-kok Sin5-ju2 thoan5-to7-chia2 Ma-ka-li-su-ta2 (Macalister) lai5 Jit8-pun2 ti7 Sin5-hou7 khai-si2 toa7 e5 kiu3 leng5 Sin5-ju2 e5 hun3-heng chu7-hoe7, goa2 chit8 e5-hng khi3 khoaN3, thau5-khak chhin-chhiuN7 hou7 kong3-thui5 kong3 tioh8, chin toa7 e5 kek-tong7, goa2 pi2 chiah e5 Bi2-kok e5 hun3-heng ka tai7-seng siu7 tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 tiau3-beng7, chong2-si7 goa2 chhin-chhiuN7 thou3-a2 tuh-ku teh khun3, chhim-chhim e5 thou2-khui3. Koh tui3 O-su-bong2 (Osborn) e5 chheh siu7 ka3-si7, su-iau3 kim3-chiah8 ki5-to2, chiu7 ka-ki7 chit8 lang5 jip8 bak8-pang5. 1952 ni5 3 geh8 1 jit8 kau3 10 jit8, cha2-tng3 kim3-chiah8 chun2-pi7 ki5-to2. 11 jit8 khi2 khai-si2 cheng3-sek e5 kim3-chiah8 ki5-to2, khi2-chhou kui2-na7 jit8 u7 kam2-kak iau kau3 tong3 be7 tiau5 e5 iu2-hek8, chong2-si7 chiap-soa3 bo5-theng5 e5 ki5-to2 u7 khah-iaN5 chit e5 iu2-hek8. Te7 6 jit8 khi2 chiu7 sim-sin5 u7 kong2 boe7 chin7 e5 peng5-an, seng3-kiat kap hoaN-hi2, Seng3 Sin5 hou7 goa2 e5 ki5-to2 chhin-chhiuN7 chui2-choaN5 tit8-tit8 chheng3 chhut-lai5. “Sin3 Goa2 e5 lang5, chhin-chhiuN7 Seng3-keng sou2 kong2, u7 oah8-chui2 e5 khoe, beh tui3 i e5 pak-lai7 lau5-chhut.” (Iok-han7 7:38)
