Tng5-tng5 e5 mi5 ke3-khi3, cha2-khi2 e5 9 tiam2-cheng, hng7-hng7 chhiu7-be2 eng-ko e5 siaN si7 lok8-hng5 chhun-thiN leng5 chiau2 e5 chan3-bi2, chit e5 kim3-chiah8 e5 be2-cham7 Chu2 tui3 goa2 kong2, “Li2 e5 kim3-chiah8 liau2 lah! I2-au7 tioh8 1 jit8 1 chiah8 chu2-gi7 lai5 cheng-chian3” Sin5-ju2 e5 sin5-jiah na2 kho2-koan chian5-chin3.
